♪Missing you cuts deep,
shaping your shadow♪

148
00:10:26,190 --> 00:10:28,670
♪All my pain comes
from not wanting to part♪

149
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:31,380
♪I was caught in the middle♪

150
00:10:31,380 --> 00:10:33,030
♪It's hard to survive♪

151
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,630
♪Love faded in you, but grew in me♪

152
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:36,310
♪And wore me down inside♪

153
00:10:36,310 --> 00:10:37,910
♪I'm the desert, craving the open sea♪

154
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:39,310
♪I'll show you the humor in tragedy♪

155
00:10:39,310 --> 00:10:42,560
♪Will you ever remember me?♪

156
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:45,880
♪A divine once blessed us with love♪

157
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:48,430
♪But that blessing faded in a flash♪

158
00:10:49,130 --> 00:10:52,360
♪The moon stays bright, never falling♪

159
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:55,530
♪But it's no longer mine♪

160
00:11:21,590 --> 00:11:26,170
♪Longing finds a heartbeat as I fall♪

161
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:33,360
♪When our eyes meet, the world softens♪

162
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:37,370
♪I cling to the past like a wanderer♪

163
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:40,990
♪Still guarding the gate
to old memories♪

164
00:11:41,190 --> 00:11:46,810
♪Eternal promise♪

165
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:55,040
♪How do I heal after losing you?♪

166
00:11:55,660 --> 00:12:01,950
♪How could I let go of all this pain?♪

167
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:07,800
♪The more I hold back,
the closer you feel♪

168
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:11,180
♪The more it hurts,
the more I break♪

169
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:16,760
♪Every snowflake feels like your kiss♪

170
00:12:17,010 --> 00:12:23,770
♪Let time pause,
let fireflies fill the sky♪

171
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:31,000
♪In your arms,
I lose focus—tears fall♪

172
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:36,180
♪And everything else just fades away♪

173
00:12:36,730 --> 00:12:39,610
♪You belong only to me♪

174
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:45,870
♪Even if we're apart, or worlds away♪

175
00:12:46,330 --> 00:12:48,510
♪None of that could ever matter♪
